.TH "mpc52xx_gpt_start_timer" 9 "mpc52xx_gpt_start_timer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mpc52xx_gpt_start_timer \- Set and enable the GPT timer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" mpc52xx_gpt_start_timer
.BI "(struct mpc52xx_gpt_priv *gpt "  ","
.BI "u64 period "  ","
.BI "int continuous "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "gpt" 12
Pointer to gpt private data structure
.IP "period" 12
period of timer in ns; max. ~130s \fI\fP 33MHz IPB clock
.IP "continuous" 12
set to 1 to make timer continuous free running
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
An interrupt will be generated every time the timer fires
